 /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Accessories Included : &lt;/strong&gt;USB Gaming Keyboard &amp;amp; Mouse / Driver Discs / Power Cord&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Operating System Provided : &lt;/strong&gt;Microsoft Windows 8 64-bit Edition&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Country of Origin : &lt;/strong&gt; USA&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Manufactactures Warranty : &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Limited Warranty &amp;amp; Lifetime Toll Free Tech Support Services&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Technical Support E-mail: techteam@cyberpowerpc.com&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Technical Support Hotline: (888) 937-5582&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'CYBERPOWERPC Gamer Ultra GUA390 with AMD FX-4100 CPU, 8GB DDR3, AMD HD7750, 2TB HDD, 24x DVD+-RW &amp;amp; Win 8 64-Bit ; 1 Year Limited Warranty &amp;amp; Lifetime Toll Free Tech Support Services/Technical Support E-mail: techteam@cyberpowerpc.com /Technical Support Hotline: (888) 937-5582', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCYBERPOWERPC\r\n\r\nGamer Xtreme GUA390\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe CYBERPOWERPC Gamer Ultra GUA390 feature’s AMD latest “bulldozer” FX 4100 quad-core CPU alongside AMD HD7750 graphics', 'CyberpowerPC,Gamer,Ultra,GUA390,Desktop,Blue,Black', '', '', '', ''),
(71, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 (7-Inch, White)', '', '&lt;p&gt;Read e-books, watch videos, and even operate your television with the Galaxy Tab 3 7.0 tablet from Samsung. Featuring a 7-inch touch display, this handy Android tablet can sync automatically with other Samsung Galaxy devices and has front- and rear-facing cameras to take pictures or video-chat with friends. Samsung''s WatchON app lets you control and share content with your Samsung 2013 Smart TV, while the Pop-Up Play feature enables you to watch a video even as you''re checking your email.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;three-fourth-col&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 300px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3070-white-1-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 7.0 Product Shot&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3070-white-1-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sync wirelessly and automatically with your other Samsung Galaxy devices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;spacer&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3070-white-5-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 7.0 Product Shot&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3070-white-5-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Offers front- and rear-facing cameras to snap a photo or video chat with a loved one.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Interact with Your Samsung 2013 Smart TV&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With Samsung''s WatchON app, you can use the 7-inch Galaxy Tab 3 as a remote control to operate your Samsung 2013 Smart TV. You can also push movies, TV shows, photo slideshows, and more wirelessly from the tablet to the TV to enjoy them on the big screen with friends and family members. Conversely, you can push content from the TV to the tablet so that you can watch it while you''re in another room.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 210px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 7.0 - control and share&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3070-white-2-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Control and share content with your Samsung 2013 Smart TV.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 210px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 7.0 - social media&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3070-white-4-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Connect social networking accounts to post, update, and share content instantly.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;In addition, the app lets you browse a channel guide and offers movie and TV show recommendations based on your viewing habits. WatchON can even tell you instantly if your favorite shows or movies are playing without you having to hunt for them in the guide.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Pop-Up Play for Easier Multitasking&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Thanks to Samsung''s Pop-Up Play feature, you can watch videos on the 7-inch Galaxy Tab 3 even while you check email, browse the web, or perform other tasks. This enables you to get things done without missing a bit of your favorite movie or TV show.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Sync with Other Samsung Galaxy Devices&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The 7-inch Galaxy Tab 3 offers the same features, settings, and user interface as other Samsung Galaxy mobile devices for a familiar and intuitive experience. It also allows you to sync wirelessly and automatically with your other Samsung Galaxy devices to get complete access to your favorite music, videos, apps, contacts, and more, just by signing in to your account.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Compact Size for Reading, Watching, or Surfing&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Just 0.39 inches thick, and weighing 0.67 pounds, Samsung''s sleek 7-inch Galaxy Tab 3 makes it easy to read an e-book when lying in bed, browse the web while sitting at the breakfast table, or catch your favorite TV show.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Send Emails and Connect with Friends&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Using the 7-inch Galaxy Tab 3, you can combine multiple email accounts into one inbox for quick access, as well as connect social networking accounts so you can post, update, and share content instantly. The tablet''s 3-megapixel rear-facing camera allows you to take photos and share them instantly on your favorite social network, while the front-facing camera makes it easy to do video-chats.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;E-Books, Games, and More at Samsung Apps&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Apps marketplace offers a variety of applications specially designed for use on your Samsung smart device. Choose from a range of apps, including entertainment, productivity, finance, travel, education, and physical training apps along with e-books, games, and mapping and navigation applications. You can also keep children entertained and learning interactively with apps designed for specific age ranges.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Product Information&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This tablet comes installed with the Android 4.1.2 Jelly Bean operating system, contains a 1.2 GHz dual-core processor, and has a 7-inch display with 1024x600 resolution, a 1.3-megapixel front-facing camera, and a 3-megapixel rear-facing camera. It is also equipped with an IR blaster so it will work as a universal remote on both your TV and cable box.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Galaxy Tab 3 offers 8 GB of onboard memory and features a microSD card slot that allows you to add up to 64 GB of additional memory (microSD card sold separately). The tablet measures 7.4 by 4.37 by 0.39 inches (H x W x D) and weighs 0.67 pounds including the battery.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;What''s in the Box&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 7.0 tablet, USB charging cable, wall adapter, and quick start guide.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Processor, Memory, and Motherboard\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hardware Platform:&lt;/strong&gt; PC&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Processor:&lt;/strong&gt; 1.2 GHz Intel Core Duo&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Number of Processors:&lt;/strong&gt; 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RAM:&lt;/strong&gt; 1 GB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RAM Type:&lt;/strong&gt; DDR2 SDRAM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\nHard Drive\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Size:&lt;/strong&gt; 8 GB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type:&lt;/strong&gt; Serial ATA&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\nCases and Expandability\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Size (LWH):&lt;/strong&gt; 0.39 inches, 4.37 inches, 7.4 inches&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weight:&lt;/strong&gt; 10.72 ounces&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\nPower\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Battery Type:&lt;/strong&gt; Nonstandard Battery&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\nWireless\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wireless Type:&lt;/strong&gt; 802.11bgn&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'Read e-books, watch videos, and even operate your television with the Galaxy Tab 3 7.0 tablet from Samsung. Featuring a 7-inch touch display, this handy Android tablet can sync aut', 'Samsung,Galaxy,Tab,3,7,Inch,White', '', '', '', ''),
(72, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 (8-Inch, Gold-Brown)', '', '&lt;p&gt;Stay in sync while you''re on the go with the Galaxy Tab 3 8.0 tablet from Samsung. This thin, lightweight Android tablet features an 8-inch screen and provides up to 10 hours of battery life on one charge, making it easy to browse the web, check email, and enjoy social networking from wherever you are. A Multi Window feature lets you see and use two apps at once. The tablet can also sync automatically with your other Samsung Galaxy devices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-2-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 8.0 - control and share&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-2-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Control and share content with your Samsung 2013 Smart TV. &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-2-l.jpg&quot;&gt;View larger&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;spacer&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-4-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 8.0 - sleek design&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-4-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;A thin, lightweight tablet you can take with you everywhere. &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-4-l.jpg&quot;&gt;View larger&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Interact with Your Samsung 2013 Smart TV&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With Samsung''s WatchON app, you can use the 8-inch Galaxy Tab 3 as a remote control to operate your Samsung 2013 Smart TV. You can also push movies, TV shows, photo slideshows, and more wirelessly from the tablet to the TV to enjoy them on the big screen with friends and family members. Conversely, you can push content from the TV to the tablet so you can watch it while you''re in another room.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;In addition, the app lets you browse a channel guide and offers movie and TV show recommendations based on your viewing habits. WatchON can even tell you instantly if your favorite shows or movies are playing without you having to hunt for them in the guide.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;View Two Apps at Once with Multi Window&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Included in the 8-inch Galaxy Tab 3 is a Multi Window feature that allows you to see and use two apps at the same time. With Multi Window, you can drag and drop images between apps, watch a presentation while taking notes, or video-chat with friends or family members while thumbing through pictures.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-3-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 8.0 - sync wirelessly&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-3-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sync wirelessly and automatically with your other Samsung Galaxy devices. &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3080-brown-3-l.jpg&quot;&gt;View larger&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Sync with Other Samsung Galaxy Devices&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The 8-inch Galaxy Tab 3 offers the same features, settings, and user interface as other Samsung Galaxy mobile devices for a familiar and intuitive experience. It also allows you to sync wirelessly and automatically with your other Samsung Galaxy devices to get complete access to your favorite music, videos, apps, contacts, and more, just by signing in to your account.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Thin, Lightweight Design for Portability&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung''s thinnest, lightest tablet, the 8-inch Galaxy Tab 3 makes it easy to listen to music, watch videos, or stay connected with friends from virtually any location. It is powered by a 1.5 GHz dual-core processor and offers up to 10 hours of battery life on one charge, along with 16 GB of memory and up to 64 GB of expandable memory thanks to a microSD card slot.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;E-Books, Games, and More at Samsung Apps&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Apps marketplace offers a variety of applications specially designed for use on your Samsung smart device. Choose from a range of apps, including entertainment, productivity, finance, travel, education, and physical training apps along with e-books, games, and mapping and navigation applications. You can also keep children entertained and learning interactively with apps designed for specific age ranges.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'This tablet comes installed with the Android 4.2 Jelly Bean operating system, contains a 1.5 GHz dual-core processor, and has an 8-inch display with 1280x800 resolution, a 1.3-megapixel front-facing camera, and a 5-megapixel rear-facing camera. It is also equipped with an IR blaster so it will work as a universal remote on both your TV and cable box.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Galaxy Tab 3 offers 16 GB of onboard memory and features a microSD card slot that allows you to add up to 64 GB of additional memory (microSD card sold separately). The tablet measures 8.24 by 4.81 by 0.27 inches (H x W x D) and weighs 0.68 pounds including the battery.', 'Stay in sync while you''re on the go with the Galaxy Tab 3 8.0 tablet from Samsung. This thin, lightweight Android tablet features an 8-inch screen and provides up to 10 hours of ba', 'Samsung,Galaxy,Tab,3,8,Inch,Gold,Brown', '', '', '', ''),
(73, 2, 'Samsung Galaxy Tab 3 (10.1-Inch, White)', '', '&lt;p&gt;Surf the web, watch videos, send email messages, and multitask on the go using the Galaxy Tab 3 10.1 tablet from Samsung. This Android tablet features a 10.1-inch touch display along with front- and rear-facing cameras so you can take pictures or video-chat with friends. Samsung''s WatchON app allows you to use the Galaxy Tab 3 to control and share content with your Samsung 2013 Smart TV.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-2-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Control and share content with Samsung 2013 Smart Tv&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-2-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Control and share content with your Samsung 2013 Smart TV. &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-2-l.jpg&quot;&gt;View larger&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;spacer&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-4-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Dot it all&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-4-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Browse the Web, share photos, and chat with friends. &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-4-l.jpg&quot;&gt;View larger&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Interact with Your Samsung 2013 Smart TV&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With Samsung''s WatchON app, you can use the 10-inch Galaxy Tab 3 as a remote control to operate your Samsung 2013 Smart TV. You can also push movies, TV shows, photo slideshows, and more wirelessly from the tablet to the TV to enjoy them on the big screen with friends and family members. Conversely, you can push content from the TV to the tablet so you can watch it while you''re in another room.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;In addition, the app lets you browse a channel guide and offers movie and TV show recommendations based on your viewing habits. WatchON can even tell you instantly if your favorite shows or movies are playing without you having to hunt for them in the guide.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-3-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Sync wirelessly with other Samsung Galaxy devices&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-3-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Sync wirelessly and automatically with your other Samsung Galaxy devices. &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/samsung-galaxy-tab-3101-white-3-l.jpg&quot;&gt;View larger&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Sync with Other Samsung Galaxy Devices&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The 10-inch Galaxy Tab 3 offers the same features, settings, and user interface as other Samsung Galaxy mobile devices for a familiar and intuitive experience. It also allows you to sync wirelessly and automatically with your other Samsung Galaxy devices to get complete access to your favorite music, videos, apps, contacts, and more, just by signing in to your account.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Browse the Web, Share Photos, and Chat with Friends&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Featuring a 1.6 GHz dual-core processor and 16 GB of onboard memory, the 10-inch Galaxy Tab 3 allows you to search and browse the web with ease, as well as watch videos, read and send email, enjoy social networking, and play online games. In addition, a 1.3-megapixel front-facing camera and the 10.1-inch, 1280x800 display make it simple to video-chat with friends and family members who live far away.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;E-Books, Games, and More at Samsung Apps&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Apps marketplace offers a variety of applications specially designed for use on your Samsung smart device. Choose from a range of apps, including entertainment, productivity, finance, travel, education, and physical training apps along with e-books, games, and mapping and navigation applications. You can also keep children entertained and learning interactively with apps designed for specific age ranges.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'This tablet comes installed with the Android 4.2 Jelly Bean operating system, contains a 1.6 GHz dual-core processor, and has a 10.1-inch display, a 1.3-megapixel front-facing camera, and a 3-megapixel rear-facing camera. It is also equipped with an IR blaster so it will work as a universal remote on both your TV and cable box.&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe Galaxy Tab 3 offers 16 GB of onboard memory and features a microSD card slot that allows you to add up to 64 GB of additional memory (microSD card sold separately). The tablet measures 9.57 by 6.93 by 0.31 inches (H x W x D) and weighs 1.12 pounds including the battery.', 'Surf the web, watch videos, send email messages, and multitask on the go using the Galaxy Tab 3 10.1 tablet from Samsung. This Android tablet features a 10.1-inch touch display alo', 'Samsung,Galaxy,Tab,3,10,1,Inch,White', '', '', '', '');
