(74, 2, 'Dell Latitude LAT10e-2633BK 10.1-Inch Tablet', '', '&lt;h4&gt;Dell Latitude 10 Windows® Tablet: Built for business, great for fun.&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Get more done and have more fun with this 10&quot; multi-touch tablet with Intel® Dual-Core Atom™ processor, Windows® 8.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Processor: Intel® Atom™ processor Z2760 1.8GHz with Intel® Burst Technology, 1.5GHz HFM, 600MHz LFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Display: 10.1&quot; IPS (1366 X 768) Wide View Angle LCD, Corning® Gorilla® Glass, Capacitive 5 Finger Touch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Memory (RAM): 2GB DDR2 SDRAM (800MHz) integrated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Storage (hard drive): 64GB of Solid State Storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Optical Drive:&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Color:&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Dell P/N: LAT10e-2633BK&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Touch and go&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Touch and go&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/dell/cnet_dell_latitude10tablet_feature_01_60.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Experience hands-on interactivity with the Latitude 10 touch functionality. The things you do with a mouse and keyboard are more intuitive with touch. Access your email and favorite websites, view and edit images, and switch between apps, all with the touch of your fingers on the screen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Dell Latitude 10 Windows&amp;amp;reg; Tablet: Built for business, great for fun.&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/dell/cnet_dell_latitude10tablet_feature_02_300.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Ultimate Windows® 8 touch experience&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nLatitude 10 combines the convenience and mobility of a Windows® 8 touch tablet with the productivity of a PC. With Windows® 8, you can stay productive with the PC applications you already use. Multitask the way you want on the 25.6 cm (10.1) HD display using multi-touch.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;On-the-go study or fun&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhether you want to stream a new movie from your couch, enjoy your favorite books at the beach or prepare a presentation, the Latitude 10 tablet has the power and portability you need.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Stay connected&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\nBe productive at home, in the office and on the road. Plus, WiFi and Bluetooth® keep you connected.\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Dell Latitude 10 Windows&amp;amp;reg; Tablet: Built for business, great for fun.&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/dell/cnet_dell_latitude10tablet_feature_03_600.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col last&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 300px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Dell Latitude 10 Windows&amp;amp;reg; Tablet: Built for business, great for fun.&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/dell/cnet_dell_latitude10tablet_hero_300.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:300px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 299px; border: 1px solid #E9E9E9;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/dell/cnet_dell_at-a-glance.gif&quot; style=&quot;height:122px; width:299px&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Latitude 10 Essentials (LAT10e-2633BK)&lt;br /&gt;\r\nat a glance...&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Processor:&lt;/strong&gt; Intel® Atom™ processor Z2760 1.8GHz with Intel® Burst Technology, 1.5GHz HFM, 600MHz LFM&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Display:&lt;/strong&gt; 10.1&quot; IPS (1366 X 768) Wide View Angle LCD, Corning® Gorilla® Glass, Capacitive 5 Finger Touch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operating system:&lt;/strong&gt; Windows 8 Home, English&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Memory (RAM):&lt;/strong&gt; 2GB DDR2 SDRAM (800MHz) integrated&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Storage (hard drive):&lt;/strong&gt; 64GB of Solid State Storage&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Video graphics:&lt;/strong&gt; Intel® Graphics Media Accelerator (533MHz)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth®:&lt;/strong&gt; Bluetooth® tied to wireless card&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preinstalled software:&lt;/strong&gt; MS OFC TRIAL,SL,TABLET&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 'Get more done with this multi-touch 10&quot; tablet featuring Windows 8 apps', 'Dell Latitude 10 Windows® Tablet: Built for business, great for fun.\r\n\r\nGet more done and have more fun with this 10" multi-touch tablet with Intel® Dual-Core Atom™ processor,', 'Dell,Latitude,LAT10e,2633BK,10,1,Inch,Tablet', '', '', '', ''),
(75, 2, 'Lenovo Ideatab A1000 7-Inch 8GB Tablet (Black)', '', '&lt;p&gt;Travel light, surf well and enjoy the music. &amp;nbsp;The new IdeaTab A1000 is the ideal travel partner at less than 1 lb and under 1/2” thin. Plus, a vibrant 7” display, 4-point multi-touch screen, Dual Dolby&amp;nbsp;Digital Plus sound and dual front facing speakers provide all the entertainment you’ll ever need on the road or at home.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Features&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;7&amp;quot; Portable Tablet:  Entertainment For Those On The Go.&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/B00CRXZPA8_lenovo_201306074_4627.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:267px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;7&quot; Portable Tablet: Entertainment For Those On The Go.&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Attention music lovers: The tablet you’ve been waiting for has arrived. The IdeaTab A1000 is a 7” tablet that’s packed with features designed to enhance music performance. From its carefully positioned speakers, engineered to optimize the stereo experience, to its Dobly&lt;sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/sup&gt;audio enhancement, the A1000 delivers a dazzling music experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Enhanced Stereo Speakers&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/B00CRXZPA8_lenovo_201306073_4627.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:350px; width:208px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Enhanced Stereo Speakers&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Enjoy an enhanced audio experience for all multimedia including video, games and music. The A1000''s dual stereo speakers are spaced apart for better stereo effects and oriented toward the front of the tablet for a richer user experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Dolby Digital Plus&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Dolby&lt;sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/sup&gt;audio enhancement allows louder, more natural, distortion-free sound – whether you''re listening through headphones or the integrated speakers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Complete Connectivity&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Micro-USB for charging and connecting peripherals plus a micro-SD card slot for convenience and easy expandability.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;USB OTG Support&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;USB OTG (On The Go) allows your tablet to charge and read other devices, such as USB memory sticks (OTG requires a special, optional cable).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;7&amp;quot; HD Display&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/B00CRXZPA8_lenovo_201306071_4627.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:350px; width:214px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;7&quot; HD Display&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The IdeaTab A1000''s HD display offers a clear and colorful viewing experience whether indoors or outside. The 72 percent color gamut screen delivers vivid video and pictures – better than many screens on more expensive tablets.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Pocket Size Comfort&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/B00CRXZPA8_lenovo_201306072_4627.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:199px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Pocket Size Comfort&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;At .45” thin and only weighing .75 lbs, the IdeaTab A1000 is a perfect size for reading, listening to music, and web-surfing – and it can easily slide into a pocket when not in use.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Comfortable Design&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/aplus/detail-page/B00CRXZPA8_lenovo_201306070_4627.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:140px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Comfortable Design&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The A1000''s &quot;ring&quot; design emphasizes its slimness while curved surfaces make it comfortable to hold.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Long Battery Life&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The A1000 offers over 7 hours of WiFi browsing on a single battery charge.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;WiFi Connectivity&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Stay connected with 802.11b/g/n WiFi and Bluetooth&lt;sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/sup&gt;3.0.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Lenovo Ideatab A1000 tablet', 'Travel light, surf well and enjoy the music. &nbsp;The new IdeaTab A1000 is the ideal travel partner at less than 1 lb and under 1/2” thin. Plus, a vibrant 7” display, 4-point', 'Lenovo,Ideatab,A1000,7,Inch,8GB,Tablet,Black', '', '', '', ''),
