(100, 2, 'SanDisk Ultra 64 GB MicroSDXC Class 10 UHS-1 Memory Card with Adapter (SDSDQU-064G-AFFP-A)', '', '&lt;h3&gt;From the Manufacturer&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Add 64 GB&lt;sup&gt;*&lt;/sup&gt; of storage to your Android-powered device or other smartphones and tablets while taking advantage of fast app performance with the SanDisk Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card. The card''s UHS Speed Class 1 rating&lt;sup&gt;**&lt;/sup&gt; facilitates Full HD&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; video capture while transfer speeds of up to 30 MB/s&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt; keep up with the demands of mobile applications. Additionally, the SanDisk Memory Zone app makes it easy to access and back up all the media you store in your phone''s memory and your memory card. This card comes with a SD adapter so you can also use it with SDXC card slots.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;three-fourth-col&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 250px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-1-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;SanDisk Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card (64 GB) Product Shot&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-1-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 250px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-2-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;SanDisk Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card (64 GB) Product Shot&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-2-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Enjoy fast app performance on Android-powered devices or other smartphones and tablets. &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-2-l.jpg&quot;&gt;View larger&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 250px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-faq-uhs-vs-u1.pdf&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Ultra High Speed Technology&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-4-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-B007WTAJTO-faq-uhs-vs-u1.pdf&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; for a brief explanation of this card''s UHS technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;UHS Speed Class 1&lt;sup&gt;**&lt;/sup&gt; Ideal for Shooting Full HD&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; Video&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The SanDisk Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card is Class 10 and UHS Speed Class 1&lt;sup&gt;**&lt;/sup&gt; rated for uninterrupted, Full HD&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; video recording on Android-powered devices or other smartphones and tablets. The card is also ideal for taking photos on the go with fast speeds that will reduce your wait time between shots.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Fast Transfer Speeds for Enhanced App Performance&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Smartphone and tablet users will appreciate the card''s exceptional app support. Fast transfer speeds improve a wide range of mobile activities, from 3-D gaming to photo editing. With transfer speeds of up to 30 MB/s&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;, the card lets you quickly move files between your PC and smartphone or tablet.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Memory Zone App&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt; Consolidates Digital Files&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The included Memory Zone app simplifies file management on your Android-powered device. This app lets you easily view, access, and back up all of your digital files from your phone''s memory, additional memory card, and cloud services in one convenient place.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Store Videos, Photos, Songs, and More&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the SanDisk Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card, you can add more storage to your smartphone or tablet and enjoy all the videos, photos, games, and music you love.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Designed for Durability&lt;sup&gt;4&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;SanDisk designed its microSDXC memory cards to withstand harsh operating conditions. The cards are waterproof; tested to withstand up to 72 hours in salt or fresh water to a depth of one meter. They are also vibration proof and can withstand up to 500 Gs of shock. The cards are designed to perform from negative 13 to 185 degrees Fahrenheit, so whether you''re in the desert or the Arctic tundra, you''ll get the shots you want.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Amazon Frustration-Free Packaging&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This product features Amazon Frustration-Free Packaging, which is recyclable. It comes without excess outer packaging materials such as hard plastic clamshell casings, plastic bindings, or wire ties. The packaging is designed to be opened without the use of a box cutter or knife, and it will protect your product just as well as traditional packaging. Products with Amazon Frustration-Free Packaging can frequently be shipped in their own boxes, without an additional shipping box, saving on resources and reducing waste. In addition, the packaging materials that are used are easily and frequently recycled, composted, or reused by our customers, and all the inks and dyes are biodegradable.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Product Information&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The SanDisk Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card works with any microSDXC compatible device. The included SD adapter allows the card to be used with SDXC compatible devices. Not all devices support the microSDXC or SDXC card format. Check with your device manufacturer for details.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The card measures 0.43 by 0.59 by 0.03 inches (H x W x D). The adapter measures 0.94 by 1.26 by 0.08 inches (H x W x D).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;What''s in the Box&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;SanDisk Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card (64 GB) and SD adapter.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;fourth-col last&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;centerImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Sandisk Logo&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/c26-SDSDQUI064GA11-sandisklogo.png&quot; style=&quot;width:210px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;center&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Ultra microSDXC UHS-I Card (64 GB)&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;At a Glance:&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;UHS Speed Class 1&lt;sup&gt;**&lt;/sup&gt; and Class 10 for Full HD&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; video recording&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Exceptional app performance for Android-powered devices and other smartphones/tablets&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Offers quick file transfers (up to 30 MB/s&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;) between PC and mobile device&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;SanDisk Memory Zone app&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt; lets you access, view, and back up digital files in one place&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Waterproof, shockproof, vibration proof, and X-ray proof&lt;sup&gt;4&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Includes SD adapter for compatibility with devices with an SDXC slot&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ships in frustration-free packaging&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table class=&quot;data&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;th colspan=&quot;8&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;h4&gt;ADD STORAGE TO YOUR MOBILE PHONE&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;and bring your digital life wherever you go&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n			&lt;/th&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CAPACITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ALBUMS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;(12 3.5-MIN MP3 SONGS)&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PHOTOS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;(EIGHT MEGAPIXEL JPEG)&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FULL HD VIDEO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;(H.264 @ 1080p)&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n			&lt;th style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APPS/GAMES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(50 MB size)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/th&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;64 GB&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;320&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;albums&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;1,600&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;photos&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;480&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;minutes&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;64&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;apps&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/dp/B009QZH7BU&quot;&gt;32 GB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;160&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;albums&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;800&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;photos&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;240&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;minutes&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;32&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;apps&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/dp/B009QZH7D8&quot;&gt;16 GB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;80&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;albums&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;400&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;photos&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;120&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;minutes&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;16&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;small&gt;apps&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;sup&gt;*&lt;/sup&gt; One gigabyte (GB) = one billion bytes. Some capacity not available for data storage.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;sup&gt;**&lt;/sup&gt; UHS Speed Class 1 designates a performance option designed to support real-time HD video recording with UHS-I enabled host devices.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; Compatible device required. Full HD video (1920x1080) and HD (1280x720) video support may vary based upon host device, file size, resolution, compression, bit rate, content, and other factors.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt; Up to 30 MB/s read speed; write speed lower. Based on internal testing; performance may be lower depending upon host device. One megabyte (MB) = one million bytes.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt; App download and installation required.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;sup&gt;4&lt;/sup&gt; See www.sandisk.com/proof for additional information and limitations.&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Perfect for today''s high-performance Android smartphone and tablet users who want to get the most out of memory-intensive activities like 3-D gaming and apps, the SanDisk Mobile Ultra microSDHC UHS-I card drives transfer speeds of up to 30MB/s for faster app response times. For shooting Full HD video and high-megapixel pictures, it delivers two times the speed of typical microSD memory cards and a class 10 rating for the highest video recording performance available. In addition, the included SanDisk Memory Zone app lets you easily view, access, and backup all of your digital files from your phone''s memory, additional memory card and cloud services all in one convenient place.', 'From the Manufacturer\r\n\r\nAdd 64 GB* of storage to your Android-powered device or other smartphones and tablets while taking advantage of fast app performance with the SanDisk Ultra', 'SanDisk,Ultra,64,GB,MicroSDXC,Class,10,UHS,1,Memory,Card,with,Adapter,SDSDQU,064G,AFFP,A', '', '', '', ''),
