(206, 2, 'Hankook Optimo H727 All-Season Tire - 225/60R17 98T', '', 'The Hankook Optimo H727 is a touring tire specifically designed for today’s luxury sedans. The computer-calculated tread design features CCT (Carbon Compounding Technology) and FSO (Footprint Shape Optimization) which afford the driver a quiet, comfortable ride along with uniform wear and long life. Hundreds of &quot;sipes&quot; and open grooves assure outstanding traction on rain-soaked or dry road, especially in tight turns. Four circumferential grooves effectively channel water away for strong wet performance, while a solid centerline rib provides solid dry traction and stability. The high sipe density on the Optimo H727 gives you an advantage in snow or ice conditions, providing hundreds of biting edges to increase grip in severe weather.', '', 'The Hankook Optimo H727 is a touring tire specifically designed for today’s luxury sedans. The computer-calculated tread design features CCT (Carbon Compounding Technology) and F', 'Hankook,Optimo,H727,All,Season,Tire,225,60R17,98T', '', '', '', ''),
