(213, 2, 'Cooler Master Hyper 212 EVO - CPU Cooler with 120mm PWM Fan (RR-212E-20PK-R2)', '', '&lt;div style=&quot;margin:10px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Cooler Master Hyper 212 EVO CPU Cooler&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Unmatched performance for the value, these are the tenants that guided Cooler Master engineers when designing the Hyper 212 EVO. Patented Continuous Direct Contact (CDC) technology ensures that the heat pipes are free of barriers while drawing heat away from the processor. A PWM fan ensures that fan speed can be intelligently controlled to ensure that it only speeds up when more cooling is necessary.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin:50px 0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; class=&quot;data&quot; style=&quot;width:800px&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/B005O65JXI_horizontal.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/B005O65JXI_001.jpg&quot; style=&quot;margin:10px 20px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HIGHLY EFFECTIVE COOLING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			4 x Direct Contact heat pipes with patented CDC (Continuous Direct Contact) technology draw heat away from the CPU quickly&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/B005O65JXI_horizontal.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/B005O65JXI_002.jpg&quot; style=&quot;margin:10px 20px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;USER &amp;amp; SYSTEM CONTROL OF FAN(S)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			A wide range PWM fan can be controlled by changing i