(241, 2, 'Lee Women''s Misses Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Jean', '', '&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 772px; margin: 0px auto;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B003WT1B86-top.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A wardrobe staple for any woman who wants comfort without sacrificing fashion, Lee''s Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Jeans are a true classic. These jeans are made of a sturdy fabric blend that feels as good as it looks and hit right at the waist for a flattering fit. The straight leg creates a classic silhouette, making these a great choice for everyday wear. Available in your choice of finishes and a range of sizes and lengths to suit your shape, Women''s Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Jeans are a must-have season after season.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 250px; float: right; margin: 0px 0px 15px 15px&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;background: url(http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B005GSYDQI-call2.jpg) repeat-y 0 0; overflow: hidden;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B005GSYDQI-call1.jpg&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding: 0px 0px 25px 0px; background: url(http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B005GSYDQI-call3.jpg) no-repeat bottom;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px 10px 0px; padding: 0px 10px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Women''s Relaxed Fit&lt;br /&gt;\r\nStraight Leg&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h6&gt;At a Glance:&lt;/h6&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Relaxed cut through the seat and thigh&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Straight leg for a classic silhouette&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Cotton/polyester/spandex blend retains shape&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Sit at natural waist&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Available in four finishes and a range of sizes and lengths&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 250px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B0051D4Q9C-1-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Women''s Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Product Shot&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B0051D4Q9C-1-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 250px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B0051D4Q9C-2-l.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Women''s Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Product Shot&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B0051D4Q9C-2-s.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;margin-left:265px&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Relaxed Cut with High Rise&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Lee''s Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Jeans offer a flexible fit that moves with you throughout the day. They feature a relaxed cut through the seat and thigh that extends to a straight leg for a clean, classic silhouette. For optimum comfort, these jeans also have a high rise to sit right at your natural waist.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Lightweight Fabric Retains Shape&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;These jeans are made with a stretchy cotton/polyester/spandex blend that allows for plenty of movement without losing its shape. The denim also has a soft feel and is durable enough to keep looking great wash after wash.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Versatile Five-Pocket Styling&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This jean has a classic five-pocket style with unadorned back pockets for a clean look. Its versatile design takes you from work to weekends without missing a beat and can easily be dressed up or down.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Variety of Finishes&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Jeans are available in four finishes from light tones like Stone to the deep, rich hues of Premium Dark and Premium Black. Petite, misses, and plus sizes and three lengths make it easy to find the pair that''s perfect for you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Tried and True Since 1889&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Lee has been delivering quality apparel for more than 100 years. The company enjoys making great-fitting, flattering products for the whole family. Lee offers styles and fits as individual as you are. Choose the cut, rise, fabric, and classic or modern outline that work for you. Whether you''re off on a weekend adventure or dressing for a day at work, Lee has a perfect pair of jeans for you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;What''s in the Box&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Women''s Relaxed Fit Straight Leg Jeans.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;width: 950px; margin: 0px auto; background:#000000; text-align:left;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;WOMEN''S JEANS BY LEE&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;float:left; border-left:1px solid black; background:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B005GSYDQI-m-left.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;float:left; background:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/dp/B003WT1B86&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Classic Fit Marilyn Straight Leg&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/img12/APPAREL/APLUSDETAIL/LEE/c26-B003WT1B86-thumb.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/dp/B003WT1B86&quot; style=&quot;color:#E88534; text-decoration: none; font-family:Arial, Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight:bold;&q