(270, 2, 'Panasonic V100K 42x Intelligent Zoom SD Camcorder (Black)', '', '&lt;h3&gt;From the Manufacturer&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;aplus&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder Compact Easy to Carry Ultra High Zoom High Image Quality POWER O.I.S., Black&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Imagine the photographic possibilities with an Intelligent 42x Zoom&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_1_lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;The Panasonic HC-V100K Camcorder''s features an Intelligent Zoom function that goes all the way up to 42x while preserving resolution&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(View Larger) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Intelligent 42x Zoom&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/42x_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:90px; width:90px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You can thank the Intelligent Zoom function for its smart, ultra-telephoto zooming abilities, bringing your subjects into your frame by 42x. Because of the V100K HD camcorder''s Intelligent Resolution Technology, you can record at high zoom rates while preserving fine image quality and resolution. You get sharp images of incredibly detailed objects - without the nuisance of blurry edges. And if you find yourself shooting indoors or in a darkly set location, don''t worry. The V100K camcorder has a high sensitivity sensor that is more susceptible than conventional sensors, making dark scenes brighter and clearer to the eye. Go on, zoom in on that far away spot that calls to you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Fully Charge Your Battery Once and Record for 155 Minutes&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_2.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;The V100K HD Camcorder can run up to 155 minutes on a single charge for times when it is difficult to recharge.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;If you need a couple of hours of recording time but you know that you will be in a spot where stopping to charge your camcorder is not an option, then travel well knowing that this battery has a longer recording time and consumes less power. All you need to do is to fully charge the video camera once and as you tour, walk around, or sit and record, know that you can shoot continuously for a little over 2.5 hours or 155 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;With a 32.5mm Wide-Angle, Get Close to that Large Group&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_3_lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_3.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;Capture the subjects you want with 32.5mm wide setting&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(View Larger) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;HD Video&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/HDVideo_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:18px; width:90px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Even if you''re recording at an event with a large group, the 31.6mm wide-angle setting fits more people and more of the background into your frame than other conventional video camera models. This is especially clever when you want to take a group photo in a small room. The camcorder fits your subjects into your framework even when you shoot from up-close. And don''t worry about missing someone''s comments or a baby''s chuckle, as the built-in mic will record it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Freeze a Moment in Time and Create a Still Image Right on your Camcorder&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_4.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;Capture the memories with rich still images while video recording&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Picture yourself recording your child at play with your new family puppy on its first day home. You can easily capture those special rich 0.9-megapixel still images while video shooting, even in zoom mode. When you playback your movie, simply cut a 0.9-megapixel still image of any scene you want thus creating an additional album of memories.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Your Hands will Shake from Joy, not from Blurry Footage&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_5_lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_5.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;Power O.I.S. ensures scenes are not blurry from hand shake&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(View Larger) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Power O.I.S.&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/powerOIS_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:90px; width:90px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With POWER O.I.S. in the Active Mode, even the slightest hand shake is corrected. High-powered zoom shots, which are highly susceptible to movement, will be sharp and clear. If you are walking and shooting a scene - whether while traveling, on a walking tour, or following your children around at a birthday party - know that minimal blurring will occur with handheld recording. Similarly, if you are adjusting your body posture to accommodate to your subject at hand, like trying to see where a butterfly goes in shrubs, POWER O.I.S. prevents blurry images while you are in your own creative director mode. Get introduced, shake hands, and shoot blur-free with the V100K HD camcorder.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;So Easy to Use because It''s So Smart&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_6_lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_6.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;The HC-V100K HD Camcorder''s Intelligent Auto adjusts to provide focused images of your subjects&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(View Larger) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;iA (Intelligent Auto)&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/iA_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:52px; width:90px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;iA (Intelligent Auto) thinks for you. This powerful function, on the V100K HD camcorder, senses your shooting conditions and automatically adjusts the settings and activates modes that will deliver optimal results. iA does the bothersome work for you making it easier to capture beautiful, well-focused images. This feature comes in handy for sudden photo opportunities that might be missed. With a quick-start time of 0.6-Sec, simply flip open the LCD and you''re ready to record. In Eco mode, the power turns off after 5 minutes of non-activity. This reduces power waste, power consumption, and enables a longer battery life. Green in its own way, it saves energy, too.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;iFrame It as You Record with a PC or MAC&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_7_lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_7.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;iFrame allows users to quickly edit in common video editing applications&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(View Larger) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;iFrame&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/iFrame_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:90px; width:90px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ideal for PC or MAC users, the V100K camcorder lets you record videos in iFrame, a quicker way to edit scenes you shoot in real-time. With iFrame, the video is in the same editing format that you would normally use, but since you''re already there, it''s a quick edit given its compatibility to this video editing software. iFrame works with a number of applications, including iMovie.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Made for Travel Time&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_8_lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_8.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;Time zone adjustment is simple with the made-for-travel HC-V100K HD Camcorder&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(View Larger) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Easily set your time, whether you are home or traveling. World Time lets you adjust your camcorder especially as you cross time zones or return home. Simply select your destination from the displayed map and the camcorder will remember your time zone. You can set the time for two different world locations - such as home and destination - and you can switch between the times by simply pressing a button.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Playback Time with your HD Video Camera&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width:280px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_9_lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Panasonic HC-V100K HD Camcorder&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/hc-v100_cf_9.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;Replay your videos on an VIERA TV via HDMI cable or SD memory card.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n(View Larger) &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Mini HDMI&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/miniHDMI_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:90px; width:90px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You''ve poured your creative juices into your projects - now, sit back and playback your work. Use a memory card or connect with a cable - either way, you are sure to have easy viewing. If your TV is HDMI-compatible, a single HDMI mini cable is all you need. When using a video component cable, you need a separate audio cable. You can also connect your HD camcorder to a VIERA or compatible Blu-ray Disc Player via an HDMI mini cable, and you can control both units in a single synchronized operation by using just one remote control. This simple technology makes your viewing pleasure smoother.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;A Panasonic Camcorder that Makes Sharing Your Photos With Your Social Media Circles Easy&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;rightImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Facebook &amp;amp; You Tube Ready&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/photo/panasonic/aplus_nov2012/uploaders02_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:35px; width:90px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Have a blog? A Facebook or YouTube account? Want to instantly upload your latest memories with your friends and followers right from your video camera? Use your PC and the included editing software HD Writer LE 1.1 in your V100K to play or edit your videos as well as archiving and uploading to Facebook or YouTube. It''s easy to add titles, rearrange scenes, include transition effects, and edit images in single frame units. You can make a copy either in the original high-definition AVCHD format, or in the standard-definition DVD-Video (MPEG-2) format. Go on, the world awaits your next share.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;emptyClear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;spacer&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\