(273, 2, 'Sunpak 620-U4STM-CPG Tripod', '', '', '4-section tri-monopod with compact pistol grip ball head. Flip lock leg locks, 4 lleg sections with leg braces for added stability. Rubber tipped feet. Compact pistol grip ball head with quick release for shooting at any angle. Weighs 4 lb and supports up to 11 lb.', '', 'Sunpak,620,U4STM,CPG,Tripod', '', '', '', ''),
