h3&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;B009A8KZLW_image_A&quot; src=&quot;http://images.amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/acer/B009A8KZLW_image_A.jpg&quot; style=&quot;border:”0”px solid black; margin:10px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Intel® Pentium® Processor delivers an exceptional balance of proven technology and exceptional value while being energy-efficient. Its ideal performance for day-to-day computing, whether in the home, classroom or in the office.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Go wired or wireless, it''s your choice: The Gateway® NE Series Notebook provides superior Gigabit Ethernet connectivity when you''re home and swift 802.11/b/g/n Wireless when you''re mobile.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			The new Windows 8 has been re-imagined to be all about you. Put what matters most right on your Start screen, and get instant access to your people, apps, sites and more, so you can spend less time searching and more time doing. Windows 8 is smooth, intuitive, and designed to let you do what you want, the way you want.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;height:240px; text-align:left; width:1024px&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;”&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Enjoyable Entertainment &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;B009A8KZLW_image_B&quot; src=&quot;http://images.amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/acer/B009A8KZLW_image_B.jpg&quot; style=&quot;border:”0”px solid black; margin:10px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The high-quality 15.6&quot; HD LED-backlit LCD Display with 720p Ultrabright™ screen is made for your favorite entertainment brining crystal-clear imagery while consuming less energy. Play the latest high-resolution movies, digital content and media for a true cinematic view.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Media Control Keys let you truly enjoy your entertainment making operation easy and an earphone/microphone jack lets you listen to music and chat with friends and family without the hassle of switching jacks.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Want to pop a movie into your NE laptop but watch it on your big screen? No problem, the SuperMulti Double-Layer DVD Drive makes it easy and a HDMI® port even gives you the option of extending your HD viewing experience to any HDMI-equipped high-def TV or digital monitor!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Integrated Intel® HD graphics deliver turbo-charged performance to bring games and entertainment to life with life-like graphics and support for the latest Microsoft® DirectX® 10.1.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;2&quot; cellspacing=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;height:240px; text-align:left; width:1024px&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;”&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Enhanced Usability &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;B009A8KZLW_image_C” border=”0” height=&quot; src=&quot;http://images.amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/acer/B009A8KZLW_image_C.jpg&quot; style=&quot;margin:10px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be social! Gateway''s Social Networks 2.0 makes connecting to today''s most popular sites a snap by instantly launching Facebook®, YouTube and Flickr with one push and a single log-in!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Pinch, flick and swirl your fingers on the Multi-Gesture Touchpad for an intuitive mouse less, navigation of web pages, photos and more.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			The comfortable keyboard extends to a independent Numeric Keypad, making number key-in''s quick and streamlining productivity.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			Multi-in-1 Media Card Reader makes file transfers and media sharing easy and convenient, cable less, tangle-free way to transfer photos and digital files from your portable devices.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			&lt;br /&gt;\r\n			With your NE Series laptop, you are secure. Just one click launches Gateway''s MyBackup solution, which makes it simple to schedule and create backups of selected files and folders or of your entire system.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n', '', 'The Gateway® NE Series Notebook exists to fulfill one goal: To be just what you need. This any day, everywhere laptop is simple to use, letting you focus on your tasks at hand. An', 'Gateway,NE56R34u,15,6,Inch,Laptop,Black', '', '', '', ''),
(33, 2, 'ASUS S400CA-DB51T 14-Inch Laptop', '', '&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;productDescriptionWrapper&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;productDescription&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;aplus&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;two-third-col&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;ASUS VivoBook S400&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:200px; width:300px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image1_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;ASUS VivoBook&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Touch. The World at Your Fingertips&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The ASUS VivoBook S400 gets even more hands on, thanks to a responsive 14.0&quot; HD touchscreen that lets you tap, swipe and pinch to zoom just like a tablet. Designed with users in mind, the VivoBook offers an incredible mobile computing experience with a stylish and easy-to-carry slim design.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;ASUS VivoBook S400 and You. Incredible Together&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col last&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Features-At-A-Glance&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Intuitive touchscreen built for incredible Windows 8 experience&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Premium brushed metallic texture with Chiclet keyboard offering high durability and elegant look&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ASUS SonicMaster Lite technology, delivering surprisingly full sound from built-in speakers&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Solid State Hybrid Drive for faster boot time and speedy data access&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;2-second Instant On resume time from hibernate&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt; mode with worry-free auto data backup when battery falls below 5%&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;32GB x 3 years free ASUS cloud storage (valued at $49.99)&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 year Accidental Damage Protection&lt;sup&gt;3&lt;/sup&gt; with 30 days Zero Bright Dot Guarantee ($99.99 value)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Touch: Move Over Keyboard and Mouse&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image2.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:225px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image2_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Touch&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Move Over, Keyboard and Mouse&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;ASUS VivoBook S400 Series unleashes the power of Windows 8 with an all-glass 14.0&quot; HD capacitive touch panel. Open up a world of functionality with a notebook that lets you double tap to open documents, swipe to browse photos, and pinch to zoom in on maps, just like you would with a smartphone or tablet. Of course, if you prefer your trusty keyboard and track pad, you''re free to use those methods as well.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;See: Designed to Impress&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image3.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image3_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;See&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Designed to Impress&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A notebook with a touchscreen is incredible in and of itself. Of course, a slim Ultrabook&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; profile with premium brushed metallic texture, hidden hinges design, and a Chiclet keyboard wouldn''t hurt either. Focusing on even the smallest details, the ASUS VivoBook S400 is set to offer high durability and an elegant look within an ultra-slim profile that matches the dynamic new standards for high-portability and intuitive computing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col last&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Perform: One..Two..And We''re Back On&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image4.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image4_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Perform&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;One..Two..And We''re Back On&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Get up to speed faster with exclusive Super Hybrid Engine II-delivering two-second instant on so you can resume from hibernate mode without delay. Data is also safe and secure with the ASUS VivoBook S400 Series which automatically backs up your data when battery level drops below 5%.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;It''s ULTRABOOK&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; Fast&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With a 24GB solid state hybrid drive cache, the ASUS VivoBook S400 delivers faster data load time and responsiveness compared to traditional hard drives.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Hear: Hear the Power&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image5.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:250px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image5_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Hear&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Hear the Power&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Featuring exclusive ASUS SonicMaster Lite technology, the ASUS VivoBook S400 delivers deeper and richer bass, a wider audio range and pristine clarity by employing larger speakers and specially designed chambers within the limited space of a notebook to allow sound waves to fully expand outwards. With proprietary software, ASUS AudioWizard, it also offers access to new dimensions of sound with selectable modes including music, movie, and even game mode fitting audio needs based on your environment and preferences.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Share: Grab It From the Cloud&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image6.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image6_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Share&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Grab It From the Cloud&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With cloud-based ASUS WebStorage, access all your documents, photos, music, and videos from any device you are on. Even better, ASUS VivoBook S400 comes with free 32GB of WebStorage cloud space for three years (valued at $49.99).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col last&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Relax, ASUS Got You Covered!&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image7.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00COQXXPC_asus_image7_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Relax, ASUS Got You Covered!&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Comprehensive Coverage&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;1-Year International Warranty&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;1-Year Accidental Damage Protection&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;30-Day zero bright dot display guarantee&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Free 2-way standard shipping&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;24/7 technical support&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;For more information, visit http://www.service.asus.com\r\n	&lt;ul&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;Covers accidental drops, spills, power surges and fire damage for the first year (valued at $99). For more information, visit http://notebookcare.asus.com/&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '&lt;h4&gt;ASUS- Top 3 Global Consumer Notebook Brand&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As the world''s top three consumer notebook brand and maker of the world''s best-selling motherboards, ASUS prides itself by making products that always &quot;START with PEOPLE.&quot; With a persistent approach to innovation, ASUS goes beyond satisfying current consumer needs to surpass expectations and spark the imaginations of people everywhere. ASUS designs and manufactures a diverse range of products as part of our relentless search for incredible, including motherboards, graphics cards, displays, desktop and all-in-one PCs, notebooks, netbooks, networking devices, servers, smartphones and tablets. Driven by innovation and committed to quality, ASUS won 4,168 awards in 2012 and recently received the recognition for the 2013 PC Magazine Reader''s Choice Award.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nview larger\r\n\r\n\r\nASUS VivoBook\r\n\r\nTouch. The World at Your Fingertips\r\n\r\nThe ASUS VivoBook S400 gets even more hands on, thanks to a responsive 14.0" HD touchsc', 'ASUS,S400CA,DB51T,14,Inch,Laptop', '', '', '', ''),
(61, 2, 'Acer Aspire V5-571P-6698 15.6-Inch Touchscreen Laptop (Silky Silver)', '', 'Finally, a light and lean computing machine with touch: the Aspire V5 Series Notebook. At only 1&quot; slim and super light, this Notebook packs potent power and graphics and even features an optical drive and handy LAN/VGA combo port, while integrating a touchscreen for exciting hands on navigation. The elegant design sports silky surfaces and takes full advantage of the touch capabilities of Windows® 8 so you can experience efficiency hands-on as you open and close programs, browse online, and breeze through photo albums—using nothing but your fingers.\r\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;B00CHGNCZ0_image_1&quot; src=&quot;http://images.amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/acer/B00CHGNCZ0_image_1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float:right; height:402px; margin:10px; width:402px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;15.6&quot; HD Widescreen CineCrystal™ LED-backlit Display:&lt;/strong&gt; (1366 x 768) resolution; 16:9 aspect ratio&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multi-touch screen, supporting 10 finger touch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2nd Generation Intel® Core™ i3-2377M Processor&lt;strong&gt;(1.5GHz, 3MB L3 cache)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Windows 8&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intel® HD Graphics &lt;/strong&gt; with 128MB of dedicated system memory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8GB DDR3 Memory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;750GB 5400RPM SATA Hard Drive&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&l