(65, 3, 'Seagate Barracuda 3 TB HDD SATA 6 Gb/s NCQ 64MB Cache 7200 RPM 3.5-Inch Internal Bare Drive ST3000DM001', '', '&lt;h3&gt;From the Manufacturer&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Seagate Barracuda Hard Drives&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;The Power of One&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Barracuda hard drives from Seagate give you with the Power of One. One terabyte per disc technology. One drive platform for every capacity need and every desktop storage application. One hard drive qualification effort. One hard drive platform to choose from. One hard drive with trusted performance, reliability, and simplicity to deliver the lowest total cost of ownership.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You no longer need to choose between low power drives, mainstream drives, or performance drives. One hard drive with 7200RPM performance and capacity points from 250GB to 3TB makes it easier than ever to choose the right drive for any need.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;half-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Size and Performance You Want&quot; class=&quot;leftImage&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/sc_b005ct56xu-01award.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:150px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;The Size and Performance You Want&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You get more bang for your buck with 1TB per disc technology. Increasing the capacity per disc means the highest capacity drives like 1TB, 2TB and 3TB become more affordable, needing fewer discs to meet your capacity needs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Your drive is up to 45% faster than the last generation thanks to Seagate OptiCache technology. OptiCache technology combines the latest advances in hard drive microprocessors, DRAM, and proprietary caching algorithms resulting in great performance improvements for you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;half-col last&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;No-Hassle Transition to 4K Technology&quot; class=&quot;leftImage&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/sc_b005ct56xu-02fourk.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:150px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;No-Hassle Transition to 4K Technology&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You don''t have worry about the transition to Advanced Format 4K technology with Seagate SmartAlign technology. With SmartAlign, 4K drives look and act just like legacy 512 byte sector hard drives which makes your adoption of Advanced Format simple.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;half-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Maximizes Hard Drive Storage Densities&quot; class=&quot;leftImage&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/sc_b005ct56xu-03maximize.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:150px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Maximizes Hard Drive Storage Densities&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You get reliable read/write performance even in tough operating environments with Seagate AcuTrac technology. AcuTrac represents new advanced hard drive technology that can accurately control reading and writing on these &quot;nano-sized&quot; tracks spinning at 7200 RPM, even in high-touch environments, such as an all-in-one PC with loud music booming through the speakers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;half-col last&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Proven Quality and Performance&quot; class=&quot;leftImage&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/sc_b005ct56xu-05proven.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:150px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Proven Quality and Performance&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Barracuda has become the world''s most popular family of hard drives with consistent quality and performance-enhancing innovations and features like native command queuing and perpendicular recording. Additionally, the legendary family of Barracuda desktop hard drives is produced using the most sophisticated manufacturing process in the industry, with a focus on environmental stewardship.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;half-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Go Beyond 2TB with DiscWizard Software&quot; class=&quot;leftImage&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/sc_b005ct56xu-04wizard.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:150px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Go Beyond 2TB with DiscWizard Software&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The sure way to get native access to hard drives bigger than 2TB is to adopt the new BIOS standard called UEFI. If you''re not there yet, Seagate has an alternative. You can now use Barracuda 3TB hard drives even using legacy PC BIOS, or Windows XP with free DiscWizard software. The free DiscWizard software allows you to configure your system to access a 3TB drive, even on legacy PC BIOS systems or Windows XP. It''s a safer, more cost-effective solution for installing 3TB hard drives.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;half-col last&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Green Where it Counts&quot; class=&quot;leftImage&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/detail-page/sc_b005ct56xu-06green.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:150px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Green Where it Counts&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Barracuda 1TB-per-disk hard drives now have advanced power modes to save more energy while in idle states--without sacrificing performance. Produced using the most sophisticated manufacturing process in the industry, with a focus on environmental stewardship, Barracuda drives comply with the RoHS directive on hazardous materials and voluntarily restrict halogen compounds. Plus, 70% or more of the materials used to build Barracuda drives are recyclable&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Seagate Barracuda 7200 Technical Specifications&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n', '', 'From the Manufacturer\r\n\r\nSeagate Barracuda Hard Drives\r\n\r\nThe Power of One\r\n\r\nBarracuda hard drives from Seagate give you with the Power of One. One terabyte per disc technology. O', 'Seagate,Barracuda,3,TB,HDD,SATA,6,Gb,s,NCQ,64MB,Cache,7200,RPM,3,5,Inch,Internal,Bare,Drive,ST3000DM001', '', '', '', ''),
(68, 3, 'CyberpowerPC Gamer Supreme SLC4400 Desktop (Blue/Black)', '', '&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;CYBERPOWERPC&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;productDescriptionWrapper&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;aplus&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Gamer Xtreme SLC4400&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://cyberpowerpc.com&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Cyberpowerpc&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_temp_06.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:80px; width:473px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Game on with the CYBERPOWERPC Gamer Supreme SLC4400 powered by an AMD FX-8150. Liquid cooled for maximum&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;speed, loaded with 16GB of RAM, and packing an NVIDIA GTX660Ti 2GB this PC is ready to take on any task.&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Ultra fast 120GB SSD and 2TB hard drive means no compromise in storage.&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 71.95%; height: 598px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Casio EX-H15&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_SLC4400.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:575px; width:944px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;none&quot; style=&quot;width: 900px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_temp_11.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:172px; width:187px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;AMD FX Processors deliver an entirely new level of performance while minimizing power usage. The AMD FX-8150 Processor features the world''s first 8-core desktop solution and a new architecture developed from the ground up. All AMD FX Processors are unlocked, overclockable and ultra compact.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/nvidia_logo.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:172px; width:193px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You can rely on the NVIDIA GeForce GTX 660 Ti''s next-generation NVIDIA Kepler GPU Architecture to deliver cutting-edge graphics, stunning 1080p HD images and rock solid performance. You can even play the latest games with tessellation technology.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/CPRM8800.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:192px; width:192px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Give your gaming PC the added boost in performance with 16GB of blazing fast DDR3 system memory. This 16GB memory kit is designed to optimize your system’s performance allowing for snappy system response and enhanced multi-tasking.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/CPHD2000.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:192px; width:192px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Get the latest in storage technology with a 2TB SATA 6.0 Gb/s interface 7200 RPM hard drive. This hard drive provides ample storage space that you can use to save in tons of files and documents.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/CPCD2000.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:192px; width:192px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Internal Blu-Ray Drive brings an amazing Blu-Ray experience to your computer. Your PC can now easily play the hottest Blu-Ray movies as this internal Blu-Ray drive comes with 12x speeds and has a support for M-DISC for ultra reliable data storage.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/liquid_cooling.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:172px; width:193px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Keep your system chilled under the most intense situations with a liquid cooling system. This liquid cooling system is maintenance free and provides extreme thermal dissipation, keeping your processor cooled for the long hours of working or gaming on your system. The included fan provides excellent airflow while keeping noise to a minimum.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/ssd_icon.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:192px; width:192px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Solid State Drive unleashes the performance potential of the SATA 6Gbps interface, leading the speed revolution in this next-generation solution. This SSD takes productivity, gaming, and multimedia applications to the next level to work in perfect symmetry with the latest enthusiast platforms.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/window8.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:100px; width:193px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Get a more beautiful, faster, and fluid computing experience on your PC with Microsoft Windows 8 64-Bit. Windows 8 lets you put the people, apps, and sites you love on your start screen giving you instantaneous access to the things you care most about. An assortment of new and improved features on Windows 8 provides enhanced productivity, connectivity, and entertainment.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Specifications&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Main Specifications&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type : &lt;/strong&gt; Personal Computer / PC&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Unit Dimension (DxWxH) : &lt;/strong&gt; 22.9&quot; x 9.3&quot; x 22.4&quot;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Shipping Dimension (DxWxH) : &lt;/strong&gt; 29&quot; x 16&quot; x 26&quot;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Unit Weight : &lt;/strong&gt; 60 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Shipping Weight : &lt;/strong&gt; 65 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Chassis : &lt;/strong&gt; Thermaltake Chaser MK-1 Full-Tower Gaming Case&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Processor : &lt;/strong&gt;AMD FX-8150 Zambezi / 3.6GHz (Max 4.2GHz)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Processor Socket : &lt;/strong&gt; Socket AM3+&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Cache Memory : &lt;/strong&gt; 8MB L2 Cache&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Motherboard : &lt;/strong&gt; AMD 970 Chipset&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Expansion Bays Total (Free) : &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;4 ( 3 ) x External - 5.25&quot;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;6 ( 4 ) x Internal - 3.5&quot;\r\n	&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt; Expansion Slots Total (Free)