yboard &amp;amp; Mouse / Driver Discs / Power Cord&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;Operating System Provided : &lt;/strong&gt;Microsoft Windows 8 64-bit Edition&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;Country of Origin : &lt;/strong&gt; USA&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;Manufactactures Warranty : &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;1 Year Limited Warranty &amp;amp; Lifetime Toll Free Tech Support Services&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Technical Support E-mail: techteam@cyberpowerpc.com&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Technical Support Hotline: (888) 937-5582&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\nCYBERPOWERPC\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nGamer Xtreme SLC4400\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nGame on with the CYBERPOWERPC Gamer Supreme SLC4400 powered by an AMD FX-8150. Liquid cooled for maximum\r\n\r\nspeed, loaded', 'CyberpowerPC,Gamer,Supreme,SLC4400,Desktop,Blue,Black', '', '', '', ''),
