(69, 3, 'CybertronPC 5150 Escape Gaming PC (3.6GHz AMD FX 4100 w/Radeon HD6670, 8GB 1333MHz DDR3, 500GB HDD, LED 6-Fan Control, Windows 7 Home, Red)', '', '&lt;p&gt;The CybertronPC 5150 Escape is ready to help you escape from the straight jacket of slow gaming. It features a 3.60 GHz AMD FX-4100 quad-core processor that''s been unlocked for easy over clocking, which is complemented by an AMD Radeon HD 6670 graphics card with 1 GB of video memory and 8 GB of installed RAM. The system stays quiet and cool thanks to the front LED fan control panel. It''s backed by a 1-year limited warranty as well as free phone-based lifetime hardware technical support. It comes pre-installed with the 64-bit version of Microsoft Windows 7 Home Premium (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/CybertronPC-Escape-1333MHz-Control-Windows/dp/B007ZKQ9XA/ref=sr_1_29?s=pc&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;qid=1373980850&amp;amp;sr=1-29&amp;amp;keywords=cyber#windows7homepremium&quot;&gt;learn more below&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 300px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-main-red-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;cybertron 5150 red&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-main-red-sm.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:333px; width:300px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;The CybertronPC 5150 Escape in red (&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-main-red-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-frontpanel-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;cybertron 5150 red&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-frontpanel-sm.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:189px; width:300px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;Front panel fan control with switchable LED lights (red version shown; &lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-frontpanel-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;right&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;10&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n					&lt;tr&gt;\r\n						&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;At a Glance&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-factbox-logo.sm.gif&quot; style=&quot;height:75px; width:217px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n					&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n					&lt;tr&gt;\r\n						&lt;td&gt;\r\n						&lt;table align=&quot;left&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;5&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;width:215px&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n								&lt;tr&gt;\r\n									&lt;td&gt;\r\n									&lt;h5&gt;CybertronPC 5150 Escape&lt;br /&gt;\r\n									At a Glance:&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n									&lt;ul&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;3.6 GHz AMD FX-4100 quad-core processor (unlocked)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;500 GB Serial ATA hard drive (7200 RPM, 3.0 GB/s)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;8 GB installed RAM&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;AMD Radeon HD 6670 graphics (1 GB)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;Dual-layer DVD±RW drive&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;7.1-channel HD audio&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;400-watt power supply&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;Included keyboard and optical wheel mouse&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;Red chassis&lt;br /&gt;\r\n										&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n										&lt;li&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/CybertronPC-Escape-1333MHz-Control-Windows/dp/B007ZKQ9XA/ref=sr_1_29?s=pc&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;qid=1373980850&amp;amp;sr=1-29&amp;amp;keywords=cyber#fullspecs&quot;&gt;full specs below&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n									&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n									&lt;/td&gt;\r\n								&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n							&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n						&lt;/table&gt;\r\n						&lt;/td&gt;\r\n					&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n					&lt;tr&gt;\r\n						&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;At a Glance&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/th/aplus/a-plus_bottom-217._V180545591_.gif&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n					&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n				&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n			&lt;/table&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;LED Front Panel Fan Control&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With the LED Front Panel Fan Control, you can easily control up to six sets of fan speeds on this CybertronPC model. It''s stylishly designed with a diamond-cut aluminum panel and dual LED colors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Unlocked AMD FX 4100 Quad-Core Processor&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Offering unparalleled multitasking and pure core performance, the new FX-series processor from AMD utilizes AMD Turbo CORE technology to automatically boost performance when you need it most to handle your workload. And it''s unlocked out of the box and overclockable with easy-to-use AMD OverDrive software.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The 3.60 GHz AMD FX 4100 processor can boost its power up to 3.8 GHz AMD Turbo CORE technology, and it features both a 4 MB L2 cache and an 8 MB L3 cache. With AMD Turbo CORE Technology, when an FX series processor is running below its thermal limit, active cores are boosted in speed to improve overall performance. This is a dynamic and automatic process--just sit back and let the AMD FX series processor deliver a great computing experience for any task.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Unlocked for Easy Overclocking&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With an unlocked FX processor and AMD Overdrive software, fine-tuned and exceptional overclocked performance are just a few mouse clicks away. Overclocking is the process of changing settings to cause a component to operate faster than the manufacturer''s specifications.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;With AMD Overdrive software, a processor can be overclocked, tested for stability and the effects directly monitored, live. For the novice, overclocking is as easy as moving a performance slider and pushing a button to auto-tune the clock settings. That''s it!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;For advanced overclockers, AMD Overdrive allows per core setting of multipliers, changing the HT multiplier, adjusting PCIe Speed, and much more. The integrated benchmark provides a reliable performance score, while the built-in stress tests determine system stability.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Radeon HD 6670 Graphics&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A solid player in the video card arena, the Radeon HD 6670 GPU has impressive features that translate directly in to a better overall gaming experience. In addition to 1 GB of video memory, it offers an 800 MHz engine clock and 1000 MHz base memory clock for raw speed, plus 480 Stream Processing Units for rendering power. Other features include Shader Model 5.0, DirectX 11 and OpenGL 4.1 support for amazing realism and immersive gaming worlds. AMD Eyefinity multi-display technology support for expansive viewing configurations (up to six simultaneous displays), and AMD HD3D technology--enabling 3D display capabilities for many PC applications and experiences.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/AMD-Eyefinity-Technology-Hero-Banner_736Wx.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:259px; width:736px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;What''s in the Box&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;CybertronPC 5150 Escape gaming PC (model GM2222 in red), keyboard, mouse, power cord, operating instructions&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Pre-Loaded Software&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Avast Antivirus Free Edition, Adobe Acrobat Reader, Ccleaner, Mozilla Firefox, Libre Office, Image burn, VLC Media Player, IZArc, Silverlight player, Adobe Flash, Java&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;a name=&quot;fullspecs&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table cellpadding=&quot;10&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;h4&gt;Key Specifications&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n			&lt;img alt=&quot;icons&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-logo-amdfxunlocked-sm.gif&quot; style=&quot;float:right; height:105px; width:120px&quot; /&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unlocked 3.6 GHz AMD FX-4100 quad-core processor&lt;/strong&gt; (3.8 GHz with Turbo CORE technology; 8 MB L3 cache)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;500 GB SATA hard drive&lt;/strong&gt; (7200 RPM, 3.0 GB/s) with RAID 0, 1, 10, JBOD compatibility&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8 GB of installed DDR3 RAM&lt;/strong&gt; (1333 MHz; maximum)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AMD Radeon HD 6670 graphics&lt;/strong&gt; with 1 GB of dedicated video RAM&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dual-layer DVD±RW drive&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gigabit Ethernet&lt;/strong&gt; (10/100/1000)&lt;img alt=&quot;icons&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/48832G_AMDr_E_RGBx.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float:right; height:105px; margin-bottom:10/px; margin-left:20px; margin-right:20px; margin-top:10/px; width:120px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions:&lt;/strong&gt; 17 x 7.5 x 19.2 inches (HxWxD)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;h4&gt;Expansion&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;ul&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;External Bays:&lt;/strong&gt; Three 5.25-inch drive bays&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internal Bays:&lt;/strong&gt; Six 3.5-inch drive bays; two 2.5-inch drive bays&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PCI Slots:&lt;/strong&gt; 1 available (1 total)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PCI Express X1 Slots:&lt;/strong&gt; 1 available (1 total)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PCI Express X16 Slots:&lt;/strong&gt; 0 available (1 total)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PS/2 Connectors:&lt;/strong&gt; 1 mouse; 1 keyboard&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;h4&gt;Ports&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;ul&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;USB Port(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 5 USB 2.0 (1 front)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VGA Port(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DVI Video Port(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HDMI Port(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RJ-45 LAN Port(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Audio Out Jack(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Line In Jack(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 1&lt;/li&gt;\r\n				&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Microphone Jack(s):&lt;/strong&gt; 2&lt;/li&gt;\r\n			&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot; cellpadding=&quot;10&quot; style=&quot;width:900px&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-internals-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;cybertron 5150 internal&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-internals-sm.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:315px; width:450px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n			&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;Inside the CybertronPC 5150 Escape (&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-internals-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/div&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-rear-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;cybertron 5150 rear&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-rear-sm.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:315px; width:384px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n			&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;Rear view (&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cybertron/cybertronpc-5150-escape-rear-lg.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/div&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n', '', 'The CybertronPC 5150 Escape is ready to help you escape from the straight jacket of slow gaming. It features a 3.60 GHz AMD FX-4100 quad-core processor that''s been unlocked for eas', 'CybertronPC,5150,Escape,Gaming,PC,3,6GHz,AMD,FX,4100,w,Radeon,HD6670,8GB,1333MHz,DDR3,500GB,HDD,LED,6,Fan,Control,Windows,7,Home,Red', '', '', '', ''),
(70, 3, 'CyberpowerPC Gamer Ultra GUA390 Desktop (Blue/Black)', '', '&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;CYBERPOWERPC&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Gamer Xtreme GUA390&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://cyberpowerpc.com&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Cyberpowerpc&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_temp_06.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:80px; width:473px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;The CYBERPOWERPC Gamer Ultra GUA390 feature’s AMD latest “bulldozer” FX 4100 quad-core CPU alongside AMD HD7750 graphics&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;for superb multitasking and multimedia performance. The GUA390 also includes 8GB of system memory and a 2TB HDD for your media files.&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 68.43%; height: 598px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Casio EX-H15&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_GUA390.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:575px; width:944px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_temp_11.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:172px; width:187px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The native 4-core desktop processor delivers unmatched multitasking and pure core performance with all-new “Bulldozer” architecture. New 32 nanometer die shrink was designed to reduce leakage for improved efficiency, increased clock rate headroom and better thermals. Watch rich, crisp HD video. Run multiple compute-intensive applications seamlessly.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_temp_12.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:172px; width:193px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;AMD Radeon HD graphics is the most versatile solution for everyday computing. Speed up your everyday computing task with Radeon HD graphics featuring AMD App Acceleration technology. Expand your workspace with AMD’s Eyefinity technology across multiple displays for working or gaming. Experience immersive High-Definition game play with DirectX 11 support for the latest gaming titles.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/amazon_product_temp_13.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:172px; width:192px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Give your gaming PC the added boost in performance with 8GB of blazing fast DDR3 system memory. This 8GB memory kit is designed to optimize your system’s performance allowing for snappy system response and enhanced multi-tasking.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/CPHD2000.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:192px; width:192px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Get the latest in storage technology with a 2TB SATA 6.0 Gb/s interface 7200 RPM hard drive. This hard drive provides ample storage space that you can use to save in tons of files and documents.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot; style=&quot;width: 200px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/cyberpower/window8.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:100px; width:193px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Get a more beautiful, faster, and fluid computing experience on your PC with Microsoft Windows 8 64-Bit. Windows 8 lets you put the people, apps, and sites you love on your start screen giving you instantaneous access to the things you care most about. An assortment of new and improved features on Windows 8 provides enhanced productivity, connectivity, and entertainment.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Specifications&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h2&gt;Main Specifications&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type : &lt;/strong&gt; Personal Computer / PC&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Unit Dimension (DxWxH) : &lt;/strong&gt; 19.6&quot; x 7.5&quot; x 16.8&quot;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Shipping Dimension (DxWxH) : &lt;/strong&gt; 25&quot; x 12.5&quot; x 21.5&quot;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Unit Weight : &lt;/strong&gt; 32 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Shipping Weight : &lt;/strong&gt; 35 lbs&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Chassis : &lt;/strong&gt; CoolerMaster Elite 431 Black / Blue Mid-Tower Gaming Case&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Processor : &lt;/strong&gt; AMD FX-4100 Zambezi / 3.6GHz (Max 3.8GHz)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Processor Socket : &lt;/strong&gt; Socket AM3+&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Cache Memory : &lt;/strong&gt; 4MB L2 Cache&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Motherboard : &lt;/strong&gt; AMD 760G C