(202, 3, 'American Racing Vintage Torq Thrust D VN105 Torq Thrust Gray Wheel with Machined Lip (15x8&quot;/5x4.5&quot;)', '', 'The American Racing Hot Rod series Torq Thrust wheels are likely one of the most well known wheel in the world. With its vintage look and timeless spoke design, the VN105 Torq Thrust D wheel continues a long history of performance and style in an unparalleled package. This wheel offers a gray finish with machined lip. Two-piece painted aluminum with center cap and a one year finish and a lifetime structural warranty. In the late ''50s, the original five-spoke American Racing Torq Thrust ® wheel was introduced. It is considered by many to be the most famous drag and hot rod wheel of all time. Now, more than 50 years later, American Racing continues its tradition of excellence in period correct and custom wheels for hot rods, muscle cars and restoration applications.', '', 'The American Racing Hot Rod series Torq Thrust wheels are likely one of the most well known wheel in the world. With its vintage look and timeless spoke design, the VN105 Torq Thru', 'American,Racing,Vintage,Torq,Thrust,D,VN105,Torq,Thrust,Gray,Wheel,with,Machined,Lip,15x8,quot,5x4,5,quot', '', '', '', ''),
