(240, 3, 'ASUS MeMO Pad Smart ME301T-A1-BL 10.1-Inch 16 GB Tablet ( Blue )', '', '&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;productDescriptionWrapper&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;productDescription&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;aplus&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;ASUS ME172V Tablet&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:250px; width:300px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;imageCaption&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image1_lg.jpg&quot;&gt;view larger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;ASUS and You. Incredible Together&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;ASUS MeMO Pad Smart ME301T&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Stand out from the crowd with the incredible beauty and style of the ASUS MeMO Pad Smart&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt;. Incredibly lightweight and thin at only 1.28 pounds and .39 inches, it practically goes anywhere you do. Available in three stunning colors, you will be the envy of whoever gazes your way whether you play the most demanding games or just want to spend a relaxing afternoon reading. It really is that smart.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Unrivaled Visual Acuity&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image2.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Unrivaled Visual Acuity&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The ASUS MeMO Pad Smart&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; ME301T features a 10.1&quot; IPS panel with TrueVivid Technology that displays images in sharp 1280 x 800 resolution and produces a 50% better and more accurate color range in 170 degree wide viewing angles so everything looks better, from anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Best-in-Class Continuous Shooting&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image3.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:300px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Best-in-Class Continuous Shooting&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Memories may fade with time, but with a photo, they''ll last forever. So look back on those memories in as much detail as possible. The ASUS MeMO Pad Smart&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; ME301T features a best in class 5 MP autofocus rear camera with 100 picture continuous burst shooting so you can make certain you capture all those can''t miss moments. With an f2.4 aperture lens, the depth of perception is greatly increased so you may even notice small details that weren''t obvious before.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col last&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Ultra Performance&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image4.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Ultra Performance&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Featuring NVIDIA Tegra 3 Quad Core Mobile Processor, ASUS MeMO Pad&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; ME301T packs major processing power into a sleek and lightweight design. Combined with the fast and fluid feel of Android 4.1 Jelly Beans and up to 8.5 hours of battery life1, you''ll find an increase in productivity, games are more responsive, apps open faster, and system wake times are nearly instantaneous.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Incredible Sound&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image5.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Incredible Sound&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Feature is the exclusive ASUS SonicMaster technology delivering crystal clear and pure sound reproduction. Couple with the special speakers design and placement, sound comes to life providing an unforgettable enjoyment. Whatever the soundtrack to your life is, play it loud and clear with ASUS MeMO Pad&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; ME301T!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Experience ASUS Cloud Storage&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image6.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Experience ASUS Cloud Storage&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Need more storage capacity? No problem. The ASUS MeMO Pad Smart&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; ME301T has 16GB of storage and endless expansion options to meet your high storage capacity needs. With the built-in micro SD &amp;amp; micro USB ports and an additional 5GB of cloud storage from ASUS WebStorage&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;, you can access large presentation files and countless music and movies to enjoy anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col last&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Get more done with Productivity Tools&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image7.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:150px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h5&gt;Get more done with Productivity Tools&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The ASUS MeMO Pad SmartTM comes loaded with tools that help you stay productive and keep organized:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SuperNote&lt;/strong&gt;: The best note taking and drawing app providing a variety of functions and easy to share&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MyLibrary&lt;/strong&gt;: ASUS designed book-reading software for your books, magazines, and news&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;App Locker&lt;/strong&gt;: Protect your privacy by locking your important apps with a password&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;App Backup&lt;/strong&gt;: Backup installed applications and the data onto an internal storage or micro SD card&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Specifications&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operating System&lt;/strong&gt;: Android 4.1 Jellybean&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Display&lt;/strong&gt;: 10.1&quot; WXGA IPS with OGS Multi-Touch Panel (1280x800)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Processor&lt;/strong&gt;: Nvidia Tegra 3 Quad Core&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wireless&lt;/strong&gt;: 802.11 a/b/g/n&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth&lt;/strong&gt;: 3.0 (WiFi+BT combo)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Storage&lt;/strong&gt;: 16GB (Plus additional ASUS Web storage: 5GB)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Camera&lt;/strong&gt;: Front 1.2MP, Rear 5MP&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speakers:&lt;/strong&gt; Stereo speakers with ASUS SonicMaster Technology&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Card Reader&lt;/strong&gt;: 1x Micro SD (support MicroSDHC and MicroSDXC)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Battery&lt;/strong&gt;: 3.75V*1 Li-Polymer battery 5070 mAh(19Wh)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimensions&lt;/strong&gt;: 263 x 181 x 10mm (W x D x H)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weight&lt;/strong&gt;: 1.28 lbs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Color&lt;/strong&gt;: Available in Midnight Blue, Crystal White, and Hot Pink&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input/ Output&lt;/strong&gt;:\r\n	&lt;ul&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;1 x Audio Jack&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;2 x High Qualify Speakers (SonicMaster);&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;1 x Micro USB port&lt;/li&gt;\r\n		&lt;li&gt;1 x Micro HDMI port&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;third-col last&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;What''s in the Box&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;ASUS MeMO Pad&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; ME1301T Tablet&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;AC Adapter &amp;amp; Power Plug&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;User Manual&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Warranty Card&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;USB Cable&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Protect your MeMO Pad&lt;sup&gt;TM&lt;/sup&gt; ME301T with official ASUS Accessory (sold separately)&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;leftImage&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;ASUS Folio Keyboard Case&quot; src=&quot;http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/electronics/asus/B00BCPIFC2_asus_image8.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:200px; width:200px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h5&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.amazon.com/dp/B00BP54KNM&quot;&gt;ASUS Folio Keyboard Case&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Tailor made for the ASUS MeMOP ad Smart ME301T Series&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Magnets quickly and securely props up your tablet as a stand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Durable polyurethane contraction, Metal bottom for protection&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Super-thin case features a full wireless Bluetooth 3.0 Keyboard&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Flexible folding design doubles as a cover and stand&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;break&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;ASUS- Top 3 Global Consumer Notebook Brand&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As the world''s top three consumer notebook brand and maker of the world''s best-selling motherboards, ASUS prides itself by making products that always &quot;START with PEOPLE.&quot; With a persistent approach to innovation, ASUS goes beyond satisfying current consumer needs to surpa