(246, 3, 'Carhartt Men''s Workwear Pocket T-Shirt K87 ', '', '&lt;div class=&quot;feature&quot; id=&quot;dp_productDescription_container_div&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;a-row feature&quot; id=&quot;productDescription_feature_div&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;a-section a-spacing-small&quot; id=&quot;productDescription&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Men''s short-sleeve workwear t-shirt is a 100% Cotton Jersey knit with a rib-knit collar, a three-button closure and a left chest pocket. It has also been designed with side-seamed construction to minimize twisting and maximize comfort. Ash fiber content is 99% Cotton/1% Polyester. Heather Grey fiber content is 90% Cotton/10% Polyester.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Carhartt''s short sleeve workwear pocket t-shirt is an all-purpose work shirt that is perfect in warm weather or for layering when it gets cold. It’s made of 6.75-ounce, 100% cotton jersey knit and features a rib-knit collar and a left chest pocket. it’s also been designed with side-seamed construction to minimize twisting and maximize comfort. ash fiber content is 99% cotton / 1% polyester. Heather gray fiber content is 90% cotton / 10% polyester.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '', 'Men''s short-sleeve workwear t-shirt is a 100% Cotton Jersey knit with a rib-knit collar, a three-button closure and a left chest pocket. It has also been designed with side-s', 'Carhartt,Men,s,Workwear,Pocket,T,Shirt,K87', '', '', '', ''),
(247, 3, 'Merrell Women''s Barefoot Pace Glove Running Shoe ', '', '&lt;div class=&quot;feature&quot; id=&quot;dp_productDescription_container_div&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;a-row feature&quot; id=&quot;productDescription_feature_div&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;a-section a-spacing-small&quot; id=&quot;productDescription&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Outside is more than just a place. Merrell knows that. It’s in their DNA, their history and the inspiration for their future. What started as a one-man bootmaking operation in 1981 has become a global calling to get Outside and get moving. Beloved by backpackers and hikers, Merrell blazed trails, creating lighter, more comfortable footwear. Evolutions in design and technology allowed runners and hikers access to multi-sport and cross-training products designed to help them go farther, faster. Thirty years later, Merrell continues to innovate new technologies focused to get you Outside, to keep you moving. Get ready to take the scenic route with Merrell.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Strike out on new adventures, clear your head or race your best time with the Pace Glove from Merrell. The latest iteration of these barefoot running shoes for women is more comfortable, keeps rocks out better and keeps your feet warmer on frosty runs in the spring and fall. The Pace Glove 2 women''s barefoot shoe delivers a reliable, close to the ground feel while stimulating and strengthening muscles and realigning posture and gait. Just like the original, it''s lightweight, fits like a glove and lets you run the way you were meant to. The Vibram sole on our minimalist running shoes connects you securely to the earth beneath your feet so you can fly down trails with confidence. Plus, the ventilated, vegan-friendly construction creates a breathable running shoe with a conscience. Finally, the DWR-treated upper repels water so you can splash through puddles and streams when you''re hiking, walking or running. Order our new women''s barefoot shoes and be ready for anything Mother Nature tests you with.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '', 'The Outside is more than just a place. Merrell knows that. It’s in their DNA, their history and the inspiration for their future. What started as a one-man bootmaking opera', 'Merrell,Women,s,Barefoot,Pace,Glove,Running,Shoe', '', '', '', ''),
(248, 3, 'ASICS Women''s GEL-Kayano 18 Running Shoe ', '', '&lt;p&gt;Lace up a perfect jog in the ASICS Kayano. This lightweight favorite features enhanced stability and a breathable mesh upper with Biomorphic Fit technology to keep you cool and reduce irritation as you go. Generous padding at the ankle offers extra cush, while a super-grippy sole lends traction you can trust in ASICS.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Count on top-of-the-line performance every time you wear the ASICS GEL-Kayano 18 running shoe. This legendary women''s running shoe has significantly decreased weight while maintaining the classic ride, comfort and stability. The full-length Guidance Line provides smooth transitions and increases efficiency; GEL cushioning lends comfort and absorbs shock. The Biomorphic FitTM upper ensures a chafe-free fit, while the Heel Clutching SystemTM provides support and a secure heel fit. The DuraSponge rubber outsole of the ASICS GEL-Kayano 18 running shoe provides reliable traction and resists abrasion.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', 'Lace up a perfect jog in the ASICS Kayano. This lightweight favorite features enhanced stability and a breathable mesh upper with Biomorphic Fit technology to keep you cool and red', 'ASICS,Women,s,GEL,Kayano,18,Running,Shoe', '', '', '', ''),
