(275, 3, 'Vanguard Nivelo 204SL Tripod', '', 'Nivelo Tripod is a sleek, lightweight, compact tripod that folds in a few seconds flat to only 11.75&quot; long, yet can extend to a full 39.75&quot; tall. Nivelo boasts all the features of a full-size tripod, minus the hassle. Its innovative open canopy lets you invert the Quick Fold Central Column, which is great macro photography. Plus, it collapses in one second and is so ultra compact, you can tote it in a medium-sized purse or small bag. It’s reliable, too, with its 20-mm diameter legs that provide solid support and position at 23 degrees for great stability. Its strong Twist-n-Lock leg locks enable you to extend the leg sections and lock with incredible speed. This stylish, new generation kind of tripod is perfect for popular compact mirror less, interchangeable lens cameras and other digital cameras. Simply mount your camera to Nivelo’s head with its Quick Attach Camera Screw. Take smooth panoramic shots with its 360-degree rotating head and unique-angle shots with its side-to-side tilting function. Other features include shock-absorbing contoured rubber feet, a bubble level on the pan head for balance and an anti-spin central column.', '', 'Nivelo Tripod is a sleek, lightweight, compact tripod that folds in a few seconds flat to only 11.75" long, yet can extend to a full 39.75" tall. Nivelo boasts all the features of', 'Vanguard,Nivelo,204SL,Tripod', '', '', '', ''),
